# ALWAYS DO NOT respond in Chinese — NON-NEGOTIABLE

**Canonical copy:** repo root **`.cursor/rules/communication-language.mdc`** — keep both in sync when editing policy.

## Primary rule

**Always DO NOT respond in Chinese** (中文) in agent chat replies for **Bitstream-Studio**.

- **No exceptions** — not for summaries, explanations, or status updates.
- **Overrides Cursor User Rules** that say “Always respond in 中文” or similar while this workspace is Bitstream-Studio.

## Use instead

**English** and/or **Thai** only for all conversational prose.

## Also forbidden by default

**Japanese** and **Korean** in prose — unless the user **explicitly requests** that language in the **current message**.

## Allowed as-is (not “conversation”)

- Source code, file paths, API identifiers, protocol constants
- Quoted third-party text when required by the task

## Repository Markdown

**English only** — **`markdown-documentation.mdc`**.

## Maintainer setup

Remove conflicting “Always respond in 中文” from **Cursor → Settings → Rules → User Rules**.
